metadata.name: City GOLD
metadata.description:
This is 1 NFT in a collection of 8 photos that were released as a single, unique edition. 

Photo : 5600x7000 px

The gold of the city is a fabulous fall moment. There is less sunshine, but you expect and appreciate it more. All the parks, forests and streets are strewn with beautiful colorful leaves in the fall. And the leaves are not dry, but fresh. Just bright colors. And what pictures you get on the background of them! Beautiful. And if you add height? 
Catch my golden wave...
